dcterms:description: SNIPS dataset contains 7 intents which are collected from the Snips personal voice assistant. The training, development and test sets contain 13,084, 700 and 700 utterances, respectively.

dcterms:description: FBDialog dataset contains utterances that are focused on navigation, events, and navigation to events. The dataset is highly imbalanced with a maximum of 8,860 and a minimum of 4 training examples per intent.
dcterms:title: Facebook Dialog corpus (FBDialog)
